text: Kofi James (born 23 December 1997) is a West Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for the Leeward Islands in the 2017–18 Regional Super50 on 12 February 2018. In October 2019, he was named in the Leeward Islands' squad for the 2019–20 Regional Super50 tournament. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Leeward Islands cricketers
